---
import GlobalLayout from "../layouts/GlobalLayout.astro";
import site from "../config.json";

const learnItems = [
  "How to build a strong financial foundation",
  "Strategies to grow and protect your wealth",
  "Leadership principles for personal and professional growth",
  "How to create a long-term legacy for your family",
  "How to align your purpose with financial success",
];
---

<GlobalLayout
  title={site.brand}
  description="Faith-driven financial education and mentorship—wealth, leadership, and legacy with Sista Grace Ajayi."
>
  <!-- 1. Hero -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-ink text-ivory">
    <div
      class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 opacity-90"
      style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse 90% 70% at 70% 0%, rgba(196, 163, 82, 0.12) 0%, transparent 50%), linear-gradient(165deg, #0B0B0F 0%, #14141A 45%, #0B0B0F 100%);"
      aria-hidden="true"
    ></div>
    <div class="relative max-w-6xl mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8 py-24 sm:py-32 lg:py-36">
      <p class="text-gold font-sans text-xs sm:text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.22em] mb-6">
        {site.brand}
      </p>
      <h1 class="font-display text-[2.1rem] sm:text-5xl lg:text-[3.25rem] font-semibold leading-[1.08] tracking-tight max-w-4xl">
        Helping You Build Wealth, Leadership, and Legacy
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-8 max-w-2xl text-lg sm:text-xl text-ivory/80 font-sans leading-relaxed">
        Faith-driven financial education and mentorship designed to help individuals and families take control of their
        future, grow with confidence, and build lasting generational wealth.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
        <a
          href="/free-training"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-gold px-8 py-3.5 text-sm font-bold text-ink shadow-lift hover:brightness-110 transition-all"
        >
          Start Your Journey
        </a>
        <a
          href="/book"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-ivory/25 px-8 py-3.5 text-sm font-semibold text-ivory hover:bg-ivory/5 transition-colors"
        >
          Book a Free Consultation
        </a>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-12 text-sm text-ivory/55 font-sans border-t border-ivory/10 pt-8 max-w-xl">
        {site.affiliation}
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 2. Problem -->
  <section class="py-20 sm:py-24 bg-ivory border-t border-ink/5" aria-labelledby="problem-heading">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 id="problem-heading" class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-semibold text-ink leading-tight">
        Most People Are Working Hard… But Still Not Getting Ahead
      </h2>
      <div class="mt-10 space-y-6 text-body/90 font-sans text-lg leading-relaxed text-left sm:text-center">
        <p>You’re doing everything right—working, saving, trying to plan for the future.</p>
        <p class="font-medium text-ink">But no one ever taught you:</p>
        <ul class="text-left sm:inline-block sm:text-left space-y-2 mx-auto max-w-md">
          <li class="flex gap-3 sm:gap-2">
            <span class="text-gold shrink-0">◆</span>
            <span>How money really works</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3 sm:gap-2">
            <span class="text-gold shrink-0">◆</span>
            <span>How to build wealth beyond a paycheck</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3 sm:gap-2">
            <span class="text-gold shrink-0">◆</span>
            <span>How to protect your income and your family</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3 sm:gap-2">
            <span class="text-gold shrink-0">◆</span>
            <span>How to create a legacy that lasts beyond you</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p class="pt-4 text-ink font-medium">
          So you stay stuck… not because you lack effort, but because you lack the right strategy.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 3. The shift -->
  <section class="py-20 sm:py-24 bg-sand/60 border-t border-ink/5" aria-labelledby="shift-heading">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8">
      <h2 id="shift-heading" class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-semibold text-ink text-center leading-tight">
        There’s a Better Way Forward
      </h2>
      <div class="mt-10 space-y-6 font-sans text-lg text-body/90 leading-relaxed">
        <p class="text-xl font-medium text-ink text-center">
          That’s where {site.principal} comes in.
        </p>
        <p>
          Through {site.brand}, she helps individuals and families:
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-gold mt-1 shrink-0">◆</span>
            <span>Understand how money works</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-gold mt-1 shrink-0">◆</span>
            <span>Build structured financial strategies</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-gold mt-1 shrink-0">◆</span>
            <span>Develop leadership and confidence</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-gold mt-1 shrink-0">◆</span>
            <span>Align their purpose with real-world results</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-center font-medium text-ink pt-2">
          This isn’t guesswork.<br />
          <span class="text-body/80 font-normal">This is guided, proven, and built for long-term impact.</span>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 4. Authority -->
  <section class="py-20 sm:py-24 bg-ink text-ivory" aria-labelledby="meet-heading">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8 grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center">
      <div class="order-2 lg:order-1 aspect-[4/5] max-w-md mx-auto lg:mx-0 rounded-2xl bg-charcoal border border-gold/20 shadow-lift overflow-hidden">
        <div class="h-full w-full flex items-center justify-center p-10 text-center">
          <p class="text-ivory/45 font-sans text-sm leading-relaxed">Portrait placeholder—replace with Sista Grace image in public/people/.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="order-1 lg:order-2">
        <h2 id="meet-heading" class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-semibold text-ivory leading-tight">
          Meet {site.principal}
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-8 font-sans text-lg text-ivory/80 leading-relaxed">
          {site.principal} is a licensed financial professional with World Financial Group (WFG), dedicated to
          empowering individuals through financial education, leadership development, and purpose-driven guidance.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-6 font-sans text-lg text-ivory/80 leading-relaxed">
          <span class="text-gold font-semibold">Her mission is simple:</span><br />
          To help people move from uncertainty to clarity—and from survival to legacy.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-10">
          <a href="/about" class="inline-flex font-sans text-sm font-bold text-gold hover:text-ivory underline underline-offset-4 transition-colors">
            Read her story →
          </a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 5. What you'll learn -->
  <section class="py-20 sm:py-24 bg-ivory border-t border-ink/5" aria-labelledby="learn-heading">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8">
      <h2 id="learn-heading" class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-semibold text-ink text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-tight">
        What You’ll Learn Inside {site.brand}
      </h2>
      <ul class="mt-14 max-w-2xl mx-auto space-y-4 font-sans text-lg text-body/90">
        {learnItems.map((line) => (
          <li class="flex gap-4 items-start rounded-xl border border-ink/8 bg-white/80 px-6 py-4 shadow-sm">
            <span class="text-gold mt-0.5 shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">◆</span>
            <span>{line}</span>
          </li>
        ))}
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 6. Programs -->
  <section class="py-20 sm:py-24 bg-sand/40 border-t border-ink/5" aria-labelledby="programs-heading">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8">
      <h2 id="programs-heading" class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-semibold text-ink text-center leading-tight">
        Start Where You Are
      </h2>
      <div class="mt-14 grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <article class="rounded-2xl border border-ink/8 bg-ivory p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lift hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col">
          <p class="text-gold text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest font-sans">Entry</p>
          <h3 class="mt-3 font-display text-xl font-semibold text-ink">Free Financial Education Session</h3>
          <p class="mt-4 font-sans text-muted leading-relaxed flex-1">
            Get clarity on your current financial position and next steps.
          </p>
          <a href="/book" class="mt-8 inline-flex font-sans text-sm font-bold text-gold-deep hover:text-ink underline underline-offset-4">
            Book Free Session →
          </a>
        </article>
        <article class="rounded-2xl border border-ink/8 bg-ivory p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lift hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col ring-1 ring-gold/20">
          <p class="text-gold text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest font-sans">Growth</p>
          <h3 class="mt-3 font-display text-xl font-semibold text-ink">Wealth &amp; Leadership Mentorship</h3>
          <p class="mt-4 font-sans text-muted leading-relaxed flex-1">
            Structured guidance to help you grow financially and personally.
          </p>
          <a href="/apply" class="mt-8 inline-flex font-sans text-sm font-bold text-gold-deep hover:text-ink underline underline-offset-4">
            Apply Now →
          </a>
        </article>
        <article class="rounded-2xl border border-ink/8 bg-ivory p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lift hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col">
          <p class="text-gold text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest font-sans">Personal</p>
          <h3 class="mt-3 font-display text-xl font-semibold text-ink">One-on-One Advisory</h3>
          <p class="mt-4 font-sans text-muted leading-relaxed flex-1">
            Personalized strategy tailored to your goals and situation.
          </p>
          <a href="/book" class="mt-8 inline-flex font-sans text-sm font-bold text-gold-deep hover:text-ink underline underline-offset-4">
            Schedule Consultation →
          </a>
        </article>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-10 text-center">
        <a href="/programs" class="font-sans text-sm font-semibold text-ink/70 hover:text-gold-deep transition-colors">
          View all programs →
        </a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 7. Social proof -->
  <section class="py-20 sm:py-24 bg-ivory border-t border-ink/5" aria-labelledby="proof-heading">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8">
      <h2 id="proof-heading" class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-semibold text-ink text-center leading-tight">
        Real People. Real Transformation.
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-center text-sm text-muted font-sans max-w-xl mx-auto">
        Early voices from education sessions and mentorship—more stories as we grow.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-14 grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        {[
          "I finally understand how to structure my finances.",
          "This changed how I think about money completely.",
          "I now have a clear path forward.",
        ].map((quote) => (
          <blockquote class="rounded-2xl border border-ink/8 bg-white p-8 shadow-sm">
            <p class="font-display text-lg text-ink/90 italic leading-relaxed">“{quote}”</p>
            <footer class="mt-6 text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-muted font-sans">Community member</footer>
          </blockquote>
        ))}
      </div>
      <p class="mt-10 text-center">
        <a href="/testimonials" class="font-sans text-sm font-semibold text-gold-deep hover:text-ink transition-colors">
          More success stories →
        </a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 8. Final CTA -->
  <section class="relative py-20 sm:py-28 bg-ink text-ivory overflow-hidden" aria-labelledby="close-heading">
    <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 opacity-30" style="background: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 20%, rgba(196,163,82,0.2), transparent 45%);" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="relative max-w-3xl mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 id="close-heading" class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-semibold leading-tight">
        Your Future Won’t Change… Until You Do
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-8 font-sans text-lg text-ivory/75 leading-relaxed">
        The difference between where you are and where you want to be is the decision to take action.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-4 font-sans text-lg text-ivory/75 leading-relaxed">You don’t have to figure it out alone.</p>
      <div class="mt-12 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
        <a
          href="/free-training"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-gold px-8 py-3.5 text-sm font-bold text-ink shadow-lift hover:brightness-110 transition-all"
        >
          Start Your Journey Today
        </a>
        <a
          href="/book"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-ivory/25 px-8 py-3.5 text-sm font-semibold text-ivory hover:bg-ivory/5 transition-colors"
        >
          Book Your Free Consultation
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</GlobalLayout>
